      "text": "He's so great.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my grandson, Jonathan, which is also great, intelligent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He got also many reward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they want both to be, I think one is taking law and business degree.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They want to prepare themselves for the course-- I mean, what they-- they have to go through essays-- whatever they call this special test they going through.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this-- the younger one's in Tucson, which is the third, I think, year of college.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- they would like to be together, so.",
      "word_count": 9
